### Get all budget groups
GET http://localhost:3000/budget-groups
Accept: application/json

### Get budget group by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/budget-groups/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new budget group
POST http://localhost:3000/budget-groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Monthly Expenses",
  "description": "Group for monthly recurring expenses",
  "color": "#FF5733"
}

### Update budget group
PUT http://localhost:3000/budget-groups/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Monthly Expenses",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "color": "#33FF57"
}

### Delete budget group
DELETE http://localhost:3000/budget-groups/1